Subject: [PATCH 4/6] feat(inplay): I1-I5 forward evidence gates and
 buyer_ready audit

Add evidence_store (feed frames, marks, CLV, paper hash tables),
feed telemetry with seq-gap tracking, I1-I5 gate evaluation, CLV settle
at FT, and wire recording through binary ingest, router marks, and
paper execution. buyer_ready now requires all I1-I5 post-deploy.
Fix feed telemetry as_dict deadlock.
