+
+## Forward evidence gates (I1–I5 → buyer_ready)
+
+Calendar-bound buyer readiness — separate from engineering scorecard (96%).
+
+| Gate | Requirement |
+|------|-------------|
+| **I1 Feed** | Binary ingest uptime ≥99%, seq gap rate ≤0.1%, p99 peel ≤1000µs |
+| **I2 Model** | MC vs CTMC L1 ≤0.05; held-out tick Brier ≤0.28 |
+| **I3 Marks** | `fetch_exchange_marks` avg coverage ≥50% in live window |
+| **I4 CLV** | n≥25 settled rows; ≥50% beat close-of-window fair |
+| **I5 Paper** | n≥25 paper executions with SHA-256 verification hash |
+
+```bash
+bash scripts/verify_inplay_evidence_gates.sh   # exit 0 = buyer_ready
+curl /api/inplay/evidence
+```
+
+**buyer_ready** = all I1–I5 pass over forward window since `HIBS_EVIDENCE_DEPLOY_DATE` (or deploy revision file).
+
+CLV audit table: `data/inplay_evidence.sqlite` → `inplay_clv_audit`. Settle at FT via `settle_fixture_evidence(row)`.
